title: ExpanDrive 5.1.7 [MAC OS X]

ExpanDrive 5.1.7 â€“ Access cloud storage just like a USB drive.

ExpanDrive builds cloud storage in every application, acts just like a USB drive plugged into your Mac. With ExpanDrive, you can securely access any remote file server directly from the Finder or even the terminal. ExpanDrive supports:
- SFTP/FTP/FTPS
- Amazon S3
- Dropbox
- WebDAV
- Rackspace Cloud Files
- Openstack Swift
- Dreamhost DreamObjects
- Google Drive
- OneDrive
-

- HP Helion
- hubiC

What's new in version 5.1.7:
- Important security update - Sparkle auto-updater framework updated to address security vulnerability.
